[[Puebla FC]] along with the rest of the Mexican first division as of 2009 a under 20 and under 17 squad which play their own individual tournaments against the opposing clubs reserved squads.The Reserve squads usually play the day before the Top Club plays the matches .
===Reserve Squads===
Puebla FC Along with the other 17 clubs consist of a first squad an '''Under 20'''<ref>[http://www.pueblafutbolclub.com.mx/sub20.php Under 2O squad]</ref> and an '''Under 17'''<ref>[http://www.pueblafutbolclub.com.mx/sub17.php Under 17 squad]</ref>  reserve squad.

